title: Still dont have my ocean week reward
body: Hi I was just wondering when I'm getting my reward. Because my sister got hers yesterday but I still dont have mine?

replies.body: I havent gotten mine yet but ty for letting us know we will get it at the end of the week

It's given out in batches and is still going. Once it's completed we'll post an article in the client.

It should complete by the end of this week.
*All of my friends have gotten theirs except me
